# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

REDUCE_FASTFLAT

=head1 DESCRIPTION

A simple recipe to process fast-ramp flatfield data associated with
science observations.

=head1 NOTES

None.

=head1 DISPLAY

None.

